ol.li: Bacula Director executes jobs off schedule to File Daemons, log transaction reports into Catalog

li.font: File Daemons on Hosts provide backup files to Storage Daemons per Director
Storage Daemon saves backed up files into storage containers
Director manages and purges files through Storage Daemons by user action, met retention period, etc.
